║         LiaisonOS Ready Kit USB Preparation Tool                   ║
║                     "Plug and Communicate"                            ║
╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

Usage: et-prepare-ready-kit <mount-point> [options]

Arguments:
